name: HENPals - To Quetzalcoatlia, From Little Old Man 1/1
description:
Dear Quetzalcoatlia, restorer of rescued codices and the one who brings the rains. This is my take on your Aztec Restoration no. 10, the owl with the staring eyes. You would not want to meet an owl so intense out there on the Road. Thanks for the endless inspiration, Quet! 

Love (pure),
Little Old Man

This is the unique 1/1 version of the piece, a personal gift to Quetzalcoatlia, to be followed by an edition of 99 that is publicly available.
